
The cli gist client writen in CoffeeScript for Node.js.

Install
=======

$ npm install -g gista

Usage
=====

# Set your token etc.
git config --global github.user Tim-Smart
git config --global github.token xxx

# Create a Public gist
$ echo "test" > gista

# Create a private gist
$ echo "test" > gista -p

# Gist some files, with a description and custom type.
$ gista -t js -p -d "Cool gist" *.js
